snippet.title: Spider Fox Development Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
An early look at gameplay from Spider Fox mid development. Spider Fox is available now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2478640/Spider_Fox/?utm_source=Youtube

A ridiculous, web slinging adventure game where you play as a Spider Fox. The Mad Scientist has made some wild animal combinations. Climb, use Grappling Webs, and other items to overcome his obstacles to save them all.
